[5] South Dakota (Minnehaha and Lincoln counties)
Date: Fri 21 Dec 2018
Source: Ketoland News [edited]
https://www.keloland.com/news/local-news/whooping-cough-shows-up-at-lincoln-high-school/1670459958


South Dakota is seeing a lot more cases of whooping cough. One place it has shown up is at Lincoln High School, in Sioux Falls. Thursday [20 Dec 2018] the district sent a note to parents, letting them know that their child may have been exposed to the illness in the past few weeks.

A November [2018] report says the state has confirmed 120 cases. That's a 700% increase compared to the last 5 years.

